OUPES smart home products can help you control household appliances easily and conveniently.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your OUPES Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "OUPES" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one OUPES account in our "OUPES smart" app;
(3). You need to have some OUPES smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "OUPES smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "OUPES Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "OUPES" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "OUPES", and you'll be navigated to OUPES login page;
(9). Input your OUPES account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,discover my devices.”
“Alexa,turn on the switch.”
“Alexa,turn off the switch.”


Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch
smart battery
